# Valgrind suppressions for fluxgraph.
#
# The shared valgrind-leak workflow runs with --gen-suppressions=all, so the
# first run per change is a triage pass: download the valgrind-log artifact,
# copy the generated suppression blocks for any CONFIRMED third-party false
# positive (protobuf / abseil / yaml-cpp static init), and paste them here.
# Never suppress a first-party "definitely lost" leak — fix it.
#
# (Intentionally empty until triage surfaces a real false positive.)
